title: The Italian Job - Money - Velvet Revolver [TPB]
description:
Velvet Revolver made their first public debut with soundtracks. 
First, they covered "Money" in Paramount Pictures' The Italian Job.

"Money" from The Italian Job Paramount Pictures features a 2003 cover of Pink Floyd's "Money".  Debut song for Velvet Revolver. Played during the movie as well as throughout the credits. Not available on the recorded CD soundtrack.
